Package: bioc
Title: BiocLite wrapper, for the lazy.
Version: 0.0.3
Date: 2015-09-27
Authors@R: person("Charles", "Joly Beauparlant",
    email = "Charles.Joly-Beauparlant@crchul.ulaval.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is a wrapper function to avoid having to source the
    biocLite everytime I need to install a package or update installed
    packages.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.2)
License: Artistic-2.0
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
